postscript.p:
Lingard, a Catholick Priest, has published the Antiquities of the Anglo-Saxon Church, John Lingard (1771–1851; DNB), The Antiquities of the Anglo-Saxon Church (1810);
                    no. 1728 in the sale catalogue of Southey’s library. The review in Quarterly Review, 7 (March 1812), 92–107, was
                    not by Turner but by Thomas Dunham Whitaker (1759–1821; DNB). which you would do well to consign to Turner’s hands
